<BLOCKQUOTE><font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">quote:</font><HR> it seems to me that NWN is only an upgraded Diablo with more players <HR></BLOCKQUOTE><P>HAHAHAHA! I don't think so! NWN is going to be moded by the player community, it was designed with that in mind. Tons of development time has gone into creating the tools to create or replicate your favorite D&D modules. Diablo is a randomly generated map set with he same mindless MOBs running around in different places on every level. DM's will be able to get involved in the game without the players knowing for sure that the DM is involved. The DM will be able to make the unexpected happen. That can be as mean as dropping a high level MOB on an unsuspecting party, or as nice as a bucket of gold pieces from heaven. The best DM's will be the ones that create a good story and RP to the hilt. If ever there was a game for Taobob, this has got to be it.<P>--------------------<P>Might I have a copper please?<BR>The Rat Minsk<BR>Ahhh, have some cheeze Rat!
